# Rules: Ant Design Splitter

- Import Ant Design `Splitter` directly from the `antd` package
- Ant Design `Splitter` code example:
  ```tsx
  <Splitter style={{ height: '100%' }}>
    <Splitter.Panel defaultSize="25%" min="20%" max="70%">
      <CategoriesFilter />
    </Splitter.Panel>
    <Splitter.Panel>
      <TodoList />
    </Splitter.Panel>
  </Splitter>
  ```